/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae2f773162b3441ccf5f574ad53a32bdb4d86ab8","tid":290531,"uid":8441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T04:20:45.000Z","msg":"T+2交收<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0d9332c8db7e2fcfd16faf35320bca671a6c124","tid":290531,"uid":67823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T05:18:13.000Z","msg":"咁撚戇鳩都買股票"},{"pid":"3fb9e35de8caface7ef86dfe5fed98e6627934ab","tid":290531,"uid":94824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T05:22:47.000Z","msg":"上面班傻撚floating balance 都唔識？<br />\nSettlement date 先扣錢都講得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5031ad2ebcf19285d299d596b46795a79d4df00","tid":290531,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T05:25:49.000Z","msg":"上次係佢食錢機存入現金找咭數，竟然唔係即時update第二日先update<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0d1ea3a99c79257707c484aaee302e94ecf3588","tid":290531,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T05:42:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上次係佢食錢機存入現金找咭數，竟然唔係即時update第二日先update<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n還卡數其他行都唔係即時check到。"},{"pid":"a45bba556f8cf72f72643e8003c079fefc06019f","tid":290531,"uid":11118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T05:50:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上面班傻撚floating balance 都唔識？<br />\nSettlement date 先扣錢都講得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n網上顯示帳面結餘，買左股票個額唔借刻顯示帳面度，但你可用結餘會扣起左。<br />\n正常情況下你只可以轉走可用結餘"}]}